title: Plug

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a plug, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front elevational view of a plug showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is a rear elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a left side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a right side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 7 is a perspective view thereof.
The broken lines in FIGS. 1 and 2 showing of internal elements of a plug is included for the purpose of illustrating only and forms no part of the claimed design.
